sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant Purchase as Purchase Orchestrator
    participant SeatInv as Seat Inventory (gRPC)
    participant TTL as seat_hold_ttl_queue
    participant DLX as seat_hold_expired_queue
    participant Consumer as DLX Consumer

    User->>Purchase: Hold seat
    Purchase->>SeatInv: HoldSeat(...)
    SeatInv-->>Purchase: holdToken + heldUntil
    Purchase->>TTL: publish expiry message
    Note over TTL: message waits for hold TTL
    TTL-->>DLX: message expires into DLX
    DLX-->>Consumer: expired hold message
    Consumer->>SeatInv: ReleaseSeat(inventoryId, userId, holdToken)
    SeatInv-->>Consumer: seat becomes available
    Note over User,Consumer: The seat returns to the pool without the user doing anything
